channel.title: Beta Testing a proxy website
channel.description:
I would greatly appreciate it if people could beta test my website for me
http://mtbhu.tiamat-studio.net/proxy/
Or this url without the word proxy for testing purposes
http://mtbhu.tiamat-studio.net/canttouchthis
If you would like to help,whenever you have time try using my proxy to bypass your school/work firewall.
Weather it works or not, if you have tested for me please post your results here.
Thanks in advance to all beta testers.
================================ = I have noticed that on my computer = = just clicking on the link from the = = Forums does not work, if this happens = = for you too, try to copy and paste = = the URL in a new tab. = ================================
EDIT: Just a little more info on the website... The original template is not mine, I got it from free proxy template site whose link you can find at the bottom of my website. I have though heavily modified the theme and plan on continuing to do so. (I like having my own stuff) I will be buying the domain "canttouchthis.org" soon (when the site is almost perfect)
TO DO: 1.Block off people using very early versions of Firefox or Internet Explorer(or make the site compatible for these browsers)
2.Add a preloader for the button so it doesn't start off blank
3.Finish beta testing
4.Get a later version of CGI proxy
5.Get a domain name and host
